# This is a monorepo (npm workspaces) - EAS Build archives from this repo
# root when building any of the 4 apps, not just that app's own folder. Each
# app's own .easignore (android/, ios/) only covers its own directory, so
# without these root-level rules, building e.g. rentwise-tenant still scans
# and uploads rentwise-admin/rentwise-owner's local Gradle caches and build
# outputs too - bloating the upload and occasionally failing outright with
# EBUSY errors on locked Gradle cache/lock files left behind by local builds.
node_modules/
**/android/.gradle/
**/android/build/
**/android/app/build/
**/ios/Pods/
**/ios/build/
**/.expo/
